TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This represents the Exception code numeric value that represents the EXCPT_REAS
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: EXCPT_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This effective date can be set and used when the ROW_ACTV_CD is set to 1.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: EFF_DT

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This term date can be set and used when the ROW_ACTV_CD is set to 1.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: TERM_DT

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: This on/off value reflects whether or not the exception is currently available
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: ROW_ACTV_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: EXCPT_ID = EXCPT_ID_in AND EFF_DT <= DATE_in AND TERM_DT >= DATE_in

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: 07/31/2013-- Added for ITPR002522 med-d regulatory project.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: in_EGWP_CLM_CD

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
ISNULL(in_UQ_QTY)
// Unit Quantity must have a value.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_Unit_Quantity
v_val_Rebate_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
ISNULL(in_NABP_VLD_CD) OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_NABP_VLD_CD)) != 'Y' OR ISNULL(in_NABP_ID)
// Check flag set earlier in processing, which indicates whether the Pharmacy if valid [for Rebates]. // Additionally, just to check, make sure a value is assigned to the Pharmacy column
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_Pharmacy_ID
v_val_LCM_CODE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
ISNULL(in_FRMLY_SRC_CD) OR IS_SPACES(in_FRMLY_SRC_CD) OR ISNULL(in_FRMLY_ID) OR IS_SPACES(in_FRMLY_ID) OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_FRMLY_ID)) = '00001' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_FRMLY_ID)) = 'Unavailabl' -- this is for RXC claims. Yes, it is Unavailabl not Unavailable OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_FRMLY_ID)) = '0'
// Formulary ID 00001 or Unavailabl are invalid. // Additionally, Formulary Source Code or Formulary ID cannot be unassigned [NULL]
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_Formulary_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
ISNULL(in_RX_NB) OR NOT IS_NUMBER(in_RX_NB) OR --ISNULL(RTRIM(REPLACECHR(0,in_RX_NB,'0',NULL))) -- Replaces all zeros with NULL, then trims any spaces, then checks for NULL in result --ISNULL(RTRIM(LTRIM(LTRIM(in_RX_NB),'0'))) -- drops leading spaces, then leading zeros, then trailing spaces, then checks for NULL in result IIF(Length(RTRIM(LTRIM(LTRIM(in_RX_NB),'0')))=0,1,0) -- drops leading spaces, then leading zeros, then trailing spaces, then checks for NULL in result OR ( LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(in_RX_NB))) < 7 OR LENGTH(LTRIM(RTRIM(in_RX_NB))) > 12)
// Rx Number cannot be unassigned [NULL], must be numeric and cannot be all zeros. Additiionally, if must be between 7 characters 12 in length.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_Rx_Number

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
NOT ISNULL(v_Duplicate_Claim_GID)
// Check if the claim is included in the list of daily duplicates. If is , then the claim is a duplicate.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_Duplicate

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
ISNULL(in_NDC_VLD_CD) OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_NDC_VLD_CD)) != 'Y' OR ISNULL(in_NHU_TYP_CD) OR ISNULL(in_NDC_ID)
// Use indicator set earlier in processing, that indicates whether the NDC is valid for Rebates. // Additionally, just in case, check the both the NHU and NDC are not unassigned [NULL]
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_NDC_Code
v_val_Drug_On_VRAP_TDRUG
v_val_Claim_Type_Mismatch

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
ISNULL(in_CLM_LVL1_ID)
// The external Claim ID is placed in CLM_LVL1_ID. This column cannot be unassigned [NULL].
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_External_Claim_ID
v_val_Too_Future
v_val_Pharmacy_Termed
v_val_Claim_GID_Dispense_Date
v_val_100pct_Copay
v_val_Direct
v_val_Pequot
v_val_FEB_COB_Paper
v_val_Incentive_Type_Code

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(isnull(:LKP.LKP_ACTV_EXCPT_ID(19,sysdate)) ,v_FALSE ,iif(:LKP.LKP_ACTV_EXCPT_ID(19,sysdate), v_TRUE,v_FALSE) ) AND IIF( NOT ISNULL(in_EXTL_SRC_CD) AND NOT ISNULL(in_BILL_ITEM_CD) , in (ltrim(rtrim(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)), 'BRXC','BALV','BQLC') AND (LTRIM(RTRIM(in_BILL_ITEM_CD)) = '582') ,v_FALSE) -- If the claim is Med-B (extl_src_cd) and BILL_ITEM_CD designates a re-ship condition, then set this expression to true.
//BSR.TF.10172 RCI Stop Hard Exception 25 Govt Claim 2016-02-18 //add logic to check the row in RCIT_EXCPT table
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_MedB_Reship

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(NOT ISNULL(in_EXTL_SRC_CD) AND NOT ISNULL(in_COB_PD_CD) ,LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) != 'RECAP' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) != 'AETMC' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) != 'QLC' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) != 'BALV' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) != 'BRXC' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) != 'BQLC' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) != 'RXA' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) != 'APMCA' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_COB_PD_CD)) != '0' AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_COB_PD_CD)) != '1' AND DECODE(in_SCND_PD_PRIM_CD,NULL,'N' ,in_SCND_PD_PRIM_CD) != 'Y' ,v_FALSE) OR IIF(NOT ISNULL(in_EXTL_SRC_CD) AND //RECAP NOT ISNULL(in_COB_PD_CD) AND NOT ISNULL(in_COPAY_SRC_CD) ,LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) = 'RECAP' AND (LTRIM(RTRIM(in_COB_PD_CD)) != '1' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_COPAY_SRC_CD)) = '2') ,v_FALSE) OR IIF(NOT ISNULL(in_EXTL_SRC_CD) AND //QLC NOT ISNULL(in_COB_PD_CD) ,(LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) = 'QLC' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) = 'AETMC' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) = 'BALV' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) = 'BRXC' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) = 'BQLC' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) = 'APMCA' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(in_EXTL_SRC_CD)) = 'RXA') AND LTRIM(RTRIM(in_COB_PD_CD)) != '1' ,v_FALSE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_Secondary_Tertiary

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
ISNULL(in_DLVY_SYS_CD)
// Delivery System cannot be unassigned [NULL]
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_Delivery_System
v_val_Member_Rebate_Discount
v_val_Vaccine
v_val_PHC_Too_Old
v_val_RXC_Government

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
ISNULL(in_EXTL_SRC_CD) OR ISNULL(in_EXTL_LVL1_ID)
// External Source Code and Level 1 contains the highest levels of the client hierarhcy. They cannot be unassigned [NULL]
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_External_Src_Lvl1

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
v_FALSE
// This is manullay set, which implies that this process does not and cannot set the excpetion. Set to false always.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_Manual_Exception
v_val_MedD

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: 07/31/2013---ITPR002522. Changed to allow blanks, nulls or any value for models X and T.
TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(isnull(:LKP.LKP_ACTV_EXCPT_ID(31,sysdate)),v_FALSE, iif(:LKP.LKP_ACTV_EXCPT_ID(31,sysdate), iif(in_DSPN_DT >= to_date('01/01/2011','MM/DD/YYYY') AND not isnull(in_BNSTG_BEG_CD) AND in(in_MODEL_TYP_CD,'G','D'),v_TRUE,v_FALSE ) , v_FALSE ) )
-- 1. if DSPN_DT >= 1/1/2011 AND MODEL_TYP_CD in 'G','D' AND BNSTG_BEG_CD IS NOT NULL then excpt 31
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_BNSTG

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: iif(isnull(:LKP.LKP_ACTV_EXCPT_ID(32,sysdate)),v_FALSE, iif(:LKP.LKP_ACTV_EXCPT_ID(32,sysdate), iif(in_DSPN_DT >= to_date('01/01/2013','MM/DD/YYYY') AND isnull(in_CT_ID) ,v_TRUE,v_FALSE ) , v_FALSE ) ) OR iif(ISNULL(in_CLT_ID) AND in_DSPN_DT>= to_date('01/01/2013','MM/DD/YYYY'), v_TRUE,v_FALSE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_CTID

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: --ITPR002522. Check the value of EGWP_CLM_CD. Set the variable value to 0 if EGWP_CLM_CD has value in E,D,W,Null else set to 1.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_EGWP_CLM_CD

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: 02/28/2016--BSR10156 - RCI-Paid Reversal Elimination - Checks for the Claim gid hit in the Paid-Reversal Pair file created at 1410J. If return value is not null set 1 else 0
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_val_PD_RVRS_PR

TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_Count_Errors_Fixable

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: v_val_Unit_Quantity + v_val_Rebate_ID + v_val_Pharmacy_ID + v_val_LCM_CODE + v_val_Formulary_ID + v_val_Rx_Number + v_val_Duplicate + v_val_NDC_Code + v_val_Claim_Type_Mismatch + v_val_External_Claim_ID + v_val_Too_Future + v_val_Pharmacy_Termed + v_val_Claim_GID_Dispense_Date + v_val_100pct_Copay + v_val_Direct + v_val_Pequot + v_val_FEB_COB_Paper + v_val_Incentive_Type_Code + v_val_MedB_Reship + v_val_Secondary_Tertiary + v_val_Delivery_System + v_val_Member_Rebate_Discount + v_val_Vaccine + v_val_PHC_Too_Old + v_val_RXC_Government + v_val_External_Src_Lvl1 + v_val_Drug_On_VRAP_TDRUG + v_val_MedD + v_val_BNSTG+ v_val_CTID+ v_val_EGWP_CLM_CD+ v_val_PD_RVRS_PR
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_Count_Errors_All
v_NRE_CLM_CD

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(v_val_Too_Future OR ISNULL(in_DSPN_DT) ,TO_DATE('01/01/1990 00:00:00') ,in_DSPN_DT)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT VRAP.RCIT_CLM_BTCH_CNTL.FEED_ID as FEED_ID , VRAP.RCIT_CLM_BTCH_CNTL.BTCH_GID as BTCH_GID FROM VRAP.RCIT_CLM_BTCH_CNTL , VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS WHERE VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.APC_STAT_CD = 'O' AND VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS.PRD_ID = VRAP.RCIT_CLM_BTCH_CNTL.AVAL_PRD_ID
